cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a method for image reconstruction using generative adversarial networks and focuses on the edge-to-image translation task. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of color domain explicitly in the model, which relates to graphics (cs.GR) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of GANs and deep learning techniques also suggests the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed method using quantitative and qualitative metrics, which relates to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
